# data/exports/

This directory stores generated JSON exports that are served to the public Astro frontend.

The following files will be generated here by the export job:
- products.json - All published products
- products/ - Individual product detail files by slug
- manufacturers.json - All manufacturers
- categories.json - All categories with hierarchy
- hubs.json - All hubs with protocol support

These files are NOT committed to git as they are:
1. Generated from the database by export jobs
2. Served via /api/exports/* endpoints
3. Consumed by the smartpicker-web (Astro) frontend at build time

To generate exports, run:
- `pnpm cli export`
- Or trigger via admin UI export button
